N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 3 ยง 203.2 - Jock k. finlayson

State Regulations

The Banking Board hereby grants permission for Jock K. Finlayson to be at the same time a director of The Royal Bank of Canada Trust

Company and a director of RoyFund Ltd., Montreal, Canada, provided that there
continue to be no business transactions between the fund and the trust
company. Notes
